    "Name": "Cavalry Attack Helicopter",
    "Details": "Introduced in 3054, the Cavalry Attack Helicopter was one of a number of VTOLs developed to fight the Clans by Michaelson Heavy Industries. Suited to hit-and-run engagements rather than front-line combat situations the Cavalry gained a reputation for flawless service when used correctly. It has since seen service in former FedCom States and minor-nobles among the Chaos March. While capable of speeds up to 162 km/h, the Cavalry doesn't rely on this alone for protection and has 3.5 tons armor. The craft can handle a direct hit from a Clan-tech ER PPC on the nose and keep flying.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Fusion: Expensive engine that works in a Vacuum.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 10/15 hexes / 300/450 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       100     15\n<b>Left</b>          90     15\n<b>Right</b>        90     15\n<b>Rear</b>         65     15\n\n<b>Total</b>      360     75</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Narrow/Low Profile</color>\n\n<color=#ffcc00> Can carry 1 Battle Armor Squads.</color>",
